  "bib_entries": {
    "16574736": {
      "title": "Dyon-Skyrmion lumps",
      "abstract": "We make a numerical study of the classical solutions of the combined system consisting of the Georgi-Glashow model and the SO(3) gauged Skyrme model. Both monopole-Skyrmion and dyon-Skyrmion solutions are found. A new bifurcation is shown to occur in the gauged Skyrmion solution sector."
